主要翻译
 
summarize [sth] # vtr (sum up at end)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 总结 zǒng jié TC Traditional Chinese 總結  
 -- The lecturer summarised everything she had said in the last ten minutes of the lecture.
 -- 讲师对自己课堂最后十分钟的所讲内容进行总结。
 
summarize [sth], also UK: summarise [sth] vtr (say briefly)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 概述 gài shù TC Traditional Chinese 概述  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 综述 gài shù，zōng shù 
 -- The chair summarized the report for the board.
 -- 主席为董事会概述了一下报告。

在这些条目还发现' summarize '：
在英文解释里：
abstract - encapsulate - outline - precis - recap - recapitulate - sum up - wrap up
中文：
总括 - 概述 - 综述 - 总结 - 概括

标题中含有单词 'summarize' 的论坛讨论：

to summarize

Could you summarize the story so far?<"So far= until now">

"I summarize" in the present tense

summarize / sum up

summarize in/into

summarize the paragraph in two sentences

<Summarize> vs <Condense> vs <Shorten>

we should reflect on and summarize all that we <did> that day

